============================================
        PROJECT DETAILS
        Egyptian Grill Restaurant Website
============================================

Made by Mazen Mohamed
صُنع بواسطة مازن محمد

============================================
1. PROJECT OVERVIEW
============================================

This is a single-page frontend website for "Mazen for Grills" (مازن للمشويات),
an authentic Egyptian grill restaurant based in Cairo since 2005. The website
features an Ancient Egyptian / pyramid-inspired design with gold and dark
desert color tones, hieroglyphic ornaments, and Egyptian-themed decorations.

============================================
2. TECHNOLOGY STACK
============================================

- Framework: React 18.3.1 with TypeScript
- Build Tool: Vite 6.3.5
- CSS Framework: Tailwind CSS v4.1.12
- UI Components: shadcn/ui (56 components) built on Radix UI primitives
- Icons: Lucide React, MUI Icons
- Animations: tw-animate-css, motion (Framer Motion)
- Fonts: Cairo (Arabic sans-serif), Amiri (Arabic serif), Noto Naskh Arabic
- Forms: React Hook Form
- Charts: Recharts
- Carousel: Embla Carousel React
- Package Manager: pnpm

============================================
3. PROJECT STRUCTURE
============================================

Root files:
  - index.html          HTML entry point (Arabic RTL)
  - package.json        Dependencies and scripts
  - vite.config.ts      Vite configuration (React + Tailwind plugins)
  - pnpm-workspace.yaml Workspace configuration
  - postcss.config.mjs  PostCSS configuration

Source files (src/):
  - main.tsx            Application entry point
  - app/App.tsx         Main application (768 lines, all sections)

Styles (src/styles/):
  - index.css           Main CSS entry
  - fonts.css           Google Fonts imports (Cairo, Amiri, Noto Naskh Arabic)
  - tailwind.css        Tailwind CSS v4 configuration
  - theme.css           Custom theme colors and design tokens
  - globals.css         Empty placeholder

Components:
  - app/components/figma/ImageWithFallback.tsx
  - app/components/ui/  (56 shadcn/ui components)

============================================
4. WEBSITE SECTIONS
============================================

1. NAVBAR
   - Fixed top navigation bar
   - Logo: Eye of Ra + "مازن للمشويات"
   - Links: الرئيسية (Home), قائمتنا (Menu), عن مازن (About),
            آراء العملاء (Reviews), تواصل معنا (Contact)
   - CTA button: اطلب الآن (Order Now)
   - Responsive with mobile hamburger menu

2. HERO SECTION
   - Full-screen hero with pyramid sunset background image
   - Star particle effect animation
   - Tagline: "منذ عام ٢٠٠٥ — القاهرة" (Since 2005 — Cairo)
   - Restaurant name: مازن للمشويات (Mazen for Grills)
   - Two CTA buttons: استعرض قائمتنا (Browse Menu), تعرّف علينا (About Us)

3. STATS BAR
   - 20+ years of excellence
   - 50+ authentic Egyptian dishes
   - 10,000+ happy customers
   - 3 branches in Cairo

4. ABOUT SECTION
   - Two-column layout (image + text)
   - Chef grilling image with "2005" floating badge
   - Restaurant history and heritage story
   - 4 feature cards: charcoal grill, fresh meat daily, Egyptian spices, 20-year chefs

5. MENU SECTION
   - Filterable tabs: All, Grills, Shawarma, Dishes, Drinks
   - 6 menu items with images, prices, descriptions, and tags
   - Items: Mazen Special Kofta (85 EGP), Lamb Ribs (140 EGP),
            Mixed Grill (195 EGP), Beef Shawarma (65 EGP),
            Molokhia with Rabbit (110 EGP), Fresh Sugar Cane Juice (25 EGP)
   - "أضف للطلب" (Add to Order) button on each item

6. GALLERY
   - 4-photo masonry grid
   - Images: Pyramids at sunset, Mazen grills, Mixed grill dish, Egyptian pyramids

7. REVIEWS
   - 3 customer testimonials (5 stars each)
   - Customers: Ahmed El-Abd, Sara Mohamed, Khaled Ibrahim
   - Pyramid background decoration

8. PYRAMID BANNER
   - Full-width banner with pyramid image
   - Quote: "الأكل المصري الأصيل — كأنك في قلب القاهرة"
     (Authentic Egyptian food — as if you're in the heart of Cairo)

9. CONTACT SECTION
   - 3 branch cards: Shobra, Maadi, Nasr City
   - Each with address, phone number, opening hours
   - "اتصل الآن" (Call Now) button per branch
   - Order/contact form: name, phone, message fields + submit button

10. FOOTER
    - Logo and restaurant name
    - Navigation links
    - Hieroglyphic border decoration
    - Copyright notice

============================================
5. DESIGN SYSTEM
============================================

Colors:
  - Background: #0e0a04 (very dark brown/black)
  - Primary/Gold: #c9952a
  - Accent/Gold light: #d4af37
  - Text light: #f5e6c0
  - Card background: #1a1206
  - Section alt background: #0d0902

Typography:
  - Amiri: Serif font for headings and restaurant name
  - Cairo: Sans-serif for body text and navigation
  - Noto Naskh Arabic: Additional Arabic support

Decorations:
  - EgyptianDivider: Gold triangle/circle ornament
  - EyeOfRa: Eye of Horus SVG icon
  - PyramidSVG: Pyramid outline SVG
  - HieroglyphBorder: Row of ancient Egyptian symbols

============================================
6. SCRIPTS
============================================

- pnpm dev    : Start development server (Vite)
- pnpm build  : Build for production (Vite build)

